OL,3,CSir Keir to face pressure from MPs to
OL,4,Cscrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has said there is
OL,7,F"no silver bullet" to end child
OL,8,Fpoverty and acknowledged the "passion"
OL,9,Fof Labour MPs considering rebelling
OL,10,Fover the continuation of the policy
OL,11,Fthat affects some 1.6 million children.
OL,13,FThe SNP has tabled an amendment, which
OL,14,Fit says is backed by Plaid Cymru, the
OL,15,FGreen Party, the SDLP, the Alliance
OL,16,FParty, and independent MPs including
OL,17,FJeremy Corbyn.
