OL,3,CSir Keir to face pressure from MPs to
OL,4,Cscrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,FKim Johnson and Rosie Duffield are
OL,7,Famong the Labour MPs who have urged
OL,8,FSir Keir to change tack, while
OL,9,FConservative Suella Braverman spoke on
OL,10,FMonday to support scrapping the limit.
OL,12,FFormer home secretary Ms Braverman
OL,13,Facknowledged that her party had
OL,14,Fintroduced the cap, but said it was
OL,15,F"aggravating child poverty, and it's
OL,16,Ftime for it to go".
