OL,3,CSir Keir to face pressure from MPs to
OL,4,Cscrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,FShe said: "Now I know about the
OL,7,Fargument 'don't have children if you
OL,8,Fcan't afford them'. For me that's not
OL,9,Fcompassionate. It's not fair. It's not
OL,10,Fthe right thing to do."
OL,12,FThe cap was introduced by then-
OL,13,FConservative chancellor George Osborne
OL,14,Fin 2015 and restricts child welfare
OL,15,Fpayments to the first two children
OL,16,Fborn to most families.
