OL,3,CSir Keir to face pressure from MPs to
OL,4,Cscrap two-child benefit cap
OL,6,FLabour backbencher Kim Johnson told
OL,7,Fthe Commons on Monday that the
OL,8,F"punitive policy needs to be consigned
OL,9,Fto the dustbin of history where it
OL,10,Fbelongs."
OL,12,FLabour MP Rosie Duffield said in a
OL,13,FSunday newspaper that the two-child
OL,14,Fbenefit cap amounts to "social
OL,15,Fcleansing" and is an "anti-feminist
OL,16,Fand unequal piece of legislation".
